ActPilotage Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of JOELY EMILY VIVEIROS of Vancouver, British Columbia, to be a member of the Pacific Pilotage Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Peter Goodwin Bernard, K.C., whose term has expired.
